  "img": "icons/magic/fire/dagger-rune-enchant-flame-strong-purple.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A nonmagical weapon you touch becomes a magic weapon. For the duration, the weapon has a +1 bonus to attack rolls. When you attack with this weapon, choose one of the following damage types: acid, cold, fire, lightning, or thunder. It deals an extra [[/r 1d4]] damage of the chosen type when it hits.</p><p><strong>At Higher Levels</strong>. When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 5th or 6th level, the bonus to attack rolls increases to +2 and the extra damage increases to [[/r 2d4]]. When you use a spell slot of 7th level or higher, the bonus increases to +3 and the extra damage increases to [[/r 3d4]].</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
